The paper deals with the problem of visual question answering, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed methods involve the use of external corpora and semantic relationships, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves empirical studies and evaluation, which are common in information retrieval (cs.IR).
